description: Describes a dataset. This operation doesn't support datasets that include uploaded files as a source.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID.

parameters.name: DataSetId
parameters.description: The ID for the dataset that you want to create. This ID is unique per Amazon Web Services Region for each Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.description: A list of tag configuration rules to apply to a dataset. All tag configurations have the OR condition. Tags within each tile will be joined (AND). At least one rule in this structure must have all tag values assigned to it to apply Row-level security (RLS) to the dataset.
